name: Samuel Okeke
profile_summary: The profile belongs to a 30-year-old man who stands tall at 6'2". He attended the University of California, Berkeley and is currently working as a Software Engineer in the Technology sector. Born in Lagos, Nigeria, he now resides in Los Angeles, California. He is fluent in English and Igbo. He is committed to values of honesty, self-improvement, and commitment. His interests include Coding, Basketball, Traveling, and Cooking. He completed his graduate studies and identifies as a Christian. In terms of politics, he leans moderate. His ultimate dating intention is to find a life partner and he prefers monogamous relationships. He identifies as straight. His ethnicity is Black African Descent. Although he doesn't have any children currently, he is open to having some in future. While he enjoys the company of dogs and it seems he doesn't have other pets. His Zodiac sign is Leo and his MBTI personality type is INTJ. When it comes to lifestyle habits, he occasionally drinks but refrains from smoking, marijuana, and other drugs. He maintains an active exercise routine.
